Description:

I want us to program a small part of the logic from the PSX video game Alundra.

We have a 4x4 grid of elements
Each element has two possible states (on/off)
When you step on an element, the adjacent tiles (up, down, left, right) change state, but NOT the tile you're standing on
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Program:

To try this program, just run: "php YourFileDirectory/LightsOut.php" on the terminal and voilà! To quit the program, just press ctrl + c on the terminal.